<br>
1. As long As Druids do not get the current CH of Clerics, Druids can ask for improvements in any thing in-between, since Cleric will alwasy be the best healer.<br>
2. The petition is to address raid-situation only.<br>
3. They also support Cleric to get a better direct heal (and maybe presumed that Cleric would get an upgrade too)<br>
<br>
What the Clerics concern now mostly is Clerics WILL BE made RAID ONLY/ or LESS desirable for xp groups, comparing to the current situation that Druid is less desirable for raids.<br>
<br>
Xp group would not want clerics in if Druids can keep up the healing, because of the offensive advantages provided by Druids.<br>
<br>
As for Clerics getting their upgrade too at the same time, Clerics always get nerfed =p<br>
<br>
I do understand that Druids need help in raid situation, but touching anything in the healing department is gonna hurt Clerics. So please find/think of other ways to amend your current situation in raids. Don't touch the healing department =)<br>
<br>
 <p><center>Lamorat 56 Outrider<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=78959>Profile</a></center>
<center>Ston 59 Templar<a href= http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=78947>Profile</a></center> <center>Fortress of Honour</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uaidonrufflefuzz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aidon Rufflefuzz</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Hobbit of Love</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/14/02 2:39:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=650.topic&index=705>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Conversation: What about Us! (State of The Druid)</span><hr size=1> I keep hearing clerics claim that they are afraid druids will take over their spots in XP groups.<br>
<br>
I do not understand this.  I don't think clerics truly comprehend just how difficult it is for a druid to find an XP group outside his own guild, and indeed sometimes within his own guild.  There simply isn't much need for a high level druid on a raid or in an XP group.<br>
<br>
People can post all the hypotheticals they want.  They can say &quot;Druids can do this this this and that&quot;.  None of that changes the simple fact that Druids can't find groups, can't do their job on high level raids, and are increasingly becoming secondary characters used soley for porting and powerlevelling.<br>
<br>
I'm tired of hearing these people who don't play a druid suggesting they know what a druid does or doesn't do while playing the game. <p><p><center><img src=http://lilyanaeq.homestead.com/files/Signatures/Aidon.jpg>
